description:
I finally got around to getting the Trident farm setup for Gem. Best of all, I found a way to automate separating the trident wielders from the regular drowns using an axolotl and a target block system.

Then we head back to work on the Frogger game where I show off a new 7-segment display I designed. We mainly focus decorating and getting the looks of our game figured out.
